libglade-1.99.12-r2 (28 May 2002)
  23 Jul 2002; Mark Guertin <gerk@gentoo.org> :
  Added ppc to keywords

  28 May 2002; Spider <spider@gentoo.org> libglade-1.99.12-r2.ebuild :
